# API Routes Directory

This directory contains Next.js API routes for server-side operations.

## Structure

- `/api/[domain]/[action].ts` - Domain-specific API endpoints
  - Example: `/api/people/create.ts`
  - Example: `/api/routes/assign.ts`

## Guidelines

- All API routes must use `serverSupabase` from `@/lib/serverSupabase`
- All inputs must be validated with Zod
- All responses should use generated database types
- Handle errors consistently and return appropriate HTTP status codes


